author: RegardedQt314
body: not sure how long it's been since you've been updated on Kendu, but the kendu chads platform hasn't been a part of the ecosystem since the CTO took place so it's not really that much of a surprise.  the previous dev had the sole access to it and when he split from the project it was on him as to whether or not to release it fully which evidently he chose not too.  this is an extremely brief summary of what happened and there's a lot more to the story than that but it's really not worth diving into.   still unfortunate yes, but it's in the past.
